item.title: If you can help get my testscape open you can be admin on my server
item.dc:creator: @doctorwho278 doctorwho278
item.description:
@doctorwho278 wrote:

go to control pannel then windows firewall and turn off firewall
then go on execptions tab and click add port then enter 43594 as the port
and “yourservername” as the name
